<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870205-0090 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:MCI Communications Corp.</HL><DD> 02/05/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS MCIC </IN><DATELINE> MCI COMMUNICATIONS CORP. (Washington)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    H. Brian Thompsonwas named executive vice president, a new position. Mr.Thompson will have responsibility for sales, marketing andthe telecommunications concern's seven U.S. divisions. Hewill remain president of MCI's Mid-Atlantic division until asuccessor is named. In addition, he will serve on thecompany's newly formed corporate management committee, whichwill be responsible for strategy and policy.</TEXT></DOC>